Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.95,0:00:06.16,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,What are these lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:09.33,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,What could these lights that shine brightly at times be?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.20,0:00:12.70,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,It seems like you can touch them and yet cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:16.67,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,So could these lights be shadows of something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:20.59,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,If they are shadows, their bodies must exist somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:27.39,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,Could things that exist somewhere else in some other world be creating these lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:29.97,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:35.52,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Let's give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:46.82,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:05.01,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,See, this is how you play with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.22,0:01:14.56,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,It's fun, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:18.90,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,Toys meant to be played by two people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:24.90,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,Before I came here, she couldn't do this even if she wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:31.45,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,I wonder what she always did when she was alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.70,0:01:36.41,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,...when she was alone in this sad world...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.91,0:01:40.92,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,If only I could shed tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.63,0:01:48.26,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,I guess winter exists even in a world like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.93,0:01:54.43,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,Does this sky lead to another world?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:02:02.69,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,Would that world, perhaps, be where I came from? The warm and lively world?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:45.79,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's Misae-san's kitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:47.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.37,0:03:55.38,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Isn't your master getting better with her moves?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:59.80,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You'll never do something like that again, got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.26,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I won't... I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:04.93,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:07.22,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,If it isn't Furukawa-san and her boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:08.47,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:10.85,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Good evening, Misae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:14.52,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(957.273,415.8)}Episode 5
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:14.52,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(527,0)\pos(960,712.5)}The Days You Were There
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:15.98,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Be gentler with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:18.78,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You're overreacting; it's just a little bruise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:24.16,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, we brought some leftover dishes for Sunohara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:28.08,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Mom packed them thinking you were lonely with Mei-chan gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.41,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Seriously? Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:35.50,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I told you. No one gets lonely at this dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:38.09,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You're right. It's too lively if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.55,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I'll bring some tea out, so sit tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:42.34,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,My appreciation for protecting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.18,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Protecting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:47.31,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,That jerk tried to sell the cat off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:51.39,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I thought I could make a quick buck if I took it to a pet shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:53.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.90,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What's the name of this kitty?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:56.86,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Nanashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:58.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Nanashi-chan, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:01.86,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Can I call you Nana-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:05.28,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,No, not Nanashi-chan. I just haven't named him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.86,0:05:05.28,Note,Note,0,0,0,,Note: Nanashi means "Nameless"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:07.41,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,And that's a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.49,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,He's nameless?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:12.58,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But isn't he your cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:19.09,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I never wanted it, but starting some time ago, it began to stay around me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:20.88,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,so I'm just taking care of it because of how things turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:23.38,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Then what's the big deal if I sell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:25.26,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Or maybe stew him up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:29.43,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Stew what up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.27,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Joking! Just joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:36.06,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,He's been attached to you for a while, hasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:36.90,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:40.15,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Do your clothes smell like catnip?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:41.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:43.90,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.03,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:47.78,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,What is everyone doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:51.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,This is rare. Tomoyo, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:53.29,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,It's not that rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:55.46,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Sakagami-san comes to visit often.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:59.17,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I come to get advice as the Student Council President.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:04.01,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,This is a perfect opportunity since this involves both Okazaki and Sunohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:08.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Eliminate all tardiness and absence from school?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:09.01,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:12.52,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Misae-san was the first female\NStudent Council President in our school's history.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:17.52,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,And she accomplished the legendary Week of No Tardiness and Absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.52,0:06:19.31,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,That sure brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:23.15,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I want to know how you united the entire school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:25.57,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I want to make it happen, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:31.45,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,It'd be really difficult, since there are two who are the biggest obstacles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:33.20,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Who could she be talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:34.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:38.71,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun's up early and going to school on time with me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:41.63,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Then that leaves Sunohara as the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.71,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Should I come to your room to wake you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:45.72,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I wish you wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:48.26,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,How did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:50.68,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I really didn't do anything special.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:56.43,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I simply said at the morning assembly to try not to be late or absent for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:59.40,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Then everyone went along with it for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:00.94,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,That's all you did?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:05.65,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,If I could say one thing, I guess not trying too hard only helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:07.74,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I don't really understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:11.78,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,If you get all worked up yourself,\Nyou'll always get someone who'll rebel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.99,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Being too eager brings negative results.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:17.25,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I see. That's a great point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:21.25,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I'm getting quite a few guests today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.25,0:07:22.00,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:23.38,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:27.72,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Don't worry about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:28.92,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Do you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:31.43,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Um, about what I asked the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:33.22,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Ah, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:36.27,Note,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}Sign: Hikarizaka Shrine Autumn Festival - 9/23 10pm
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:34.64,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:38.23,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,An Autumn Fest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:39.14,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:43.52,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,It's a festival that's been around for a while that wishes for peace and happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:45.86,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I think it's a good choice for your first date.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:47.53,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I-I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.53,0:07:48.86,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Misae-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:50.78,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,You're a lifesaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:53.53,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,He was asking for advice for where to go on his date.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:56.54,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Stop it already. You shouldn't be eavesdropping like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:59.62,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,She's right. Everyone needs privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:00.29,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Don't be such killjoys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:02.12,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.12,0:08:03.58,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You're very welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:10.47,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:14.39,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Sunohara-san was eavesdropping on the date plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:18.02,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Divine retribution!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:24.77,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Misae-san, you're being relied on by many students.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:27.90,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,How admirable. I would like to become like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:31.99,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I've been that kind of person for a long time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:33.16,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:35.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It means you're charismatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:38.41,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There are a lot of guys who are fans of yours in my class, too. {ep 4}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:41.37,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,It's great that I'm liked, {ep 4}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:44.88,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,but I don't know what they see in a woman who only yells. {ep 4}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:50.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You don't just yell. You worry about others, which is the good part.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:57.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,And, this is something someone on the\Nrugby club said, you have a good smell of soap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:02.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,In this dirty boy's dorm,\Nyou've become an idol-like figure. {ep 4}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:04.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Like a jewel in a dunghill. {ep 4}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.65,0:09:10.19,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Yell... and worry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:12.45,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,And a good smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:14.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:16.16,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:18.95,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,It's just that someone said\Na similar thing to me in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:20.70,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I was just remembering that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.71,0:09:24.17,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Thank you for your advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.17,0:09:25.12,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Sorry I bothered you at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:27.96,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,It's fine. Come anytime you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:29.38,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I will visit again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:36.09,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Sunohara, you go back to your room, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:37.14,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:39.18,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,There's still time before lights-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:42.14,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I've got something to talk about with these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:42.89,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You're unwanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:45.90,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Can you be more direct than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:49.86,Note,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}Sign: Hikarizaka Shrine Autumn Festival - 9/23 10pm
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:49.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Go to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:55.57,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Yup. Sunohara was saying that you rarely take Furukawa-san out on dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:58.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's our problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:10:02.50,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,If you're saying something like that,\Nsome other guy will snatch Furukawa-san away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:04.37,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Th-That won't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:06.92,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I won't be snatched away by anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:15.38,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Look. You won't find another girl who would say something like that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:17.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why are you bringing up something like this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:22.72,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Looking at you two reminded me of my wonderful youthful days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.77,0:10:26.60,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're still young, Misae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:27.81,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:31.02,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,But I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:36.03,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Right now, my role is to take care of you younglings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:39.37,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:42.12,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Hang around a bit more, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:43.99,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I'll make another pot of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:52.25,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What was this school like when you were the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:54.09,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:55.21,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,It was an ordinary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:58.22,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sure you had lots of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:11:02.60,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Yeah. It was lively every day, keeping me entertained.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:04.81,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Getting hurt... Getting worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:07.31,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,But I'm still...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:10.56,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Listen well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:13.23,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,This charm has a light in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:17.24,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,It's a light that grants any one wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:22.12,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,You will take this and go to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:26.20,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,And you will grant her wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:28.25,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:51.27,Note,Sign,0,0,0,,Sign: Hikarizaka Private High School
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.28,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Igarashi-kun! Are you on your way home now, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:07.04,Default,Iga,0,0,0,,Yeah. You, too, Sagara?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:09.04,Default,Iga,0,0,0,,Yeah, what a coincidence. {ep 4}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:11.37,Default,Iga,0,0,0,,You know, if you don't mind-{ep 4}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:12.42,Default,Iga,0,0,0,,Who's he? {ep 4}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:15.00,Default,Iga,0,0,0,,Looks like he's from a different school. {ep 4}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:17.55,Default,Iga,0,0,0,,Is he your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:22.05,Default,Iga,0,0,0,,I guess I shouldn't intrude.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.05,Default,Iga,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:25.85,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Ah, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:30.18,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Um, you're Sagara Misae-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:31.94,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:33.40,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I'm Shima Katsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:35.52,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Don't I look familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:41.99,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:43.41,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I will not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:47.08,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I don't know you, nor do I see a reason for you to pay me back at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:49.87,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Maybe you don't, but I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:53.92,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Maybe you do, but I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:59.38,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Besides, because of you, he misunderstood! {ep 4}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:03.68,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I've had enough. I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:05.05,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.26,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Tell me your wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.64,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:11.64,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I came to grant your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:14.06,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,So I can't go home until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:16.27,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Then stop standing in front of me right this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:18.65,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:22.19,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,If... If that really is what you wish for, then I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:24.99,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,But that won't really satisfy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:28.95,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Since you took such good care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:35.04,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,It was back when I was in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:40.84,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I think you were going to\Nthe hospital to visit your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:46.05,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,When you went, you cheered me up when you found me in the hospital's courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:48.14,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,You don't remember this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:51.60,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I was in a wheelchair with a cat on my lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:54.44,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:13:55.10,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,You do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:57.86,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,But I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:13:59.82,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,We only spoke for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:01.32,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:04.53,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,You really cheered me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:06.95,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,What exactly did I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:08.99,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:11.45,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:14.00,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,But I really am grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.96,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,That's why I want to return the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:18.54,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Then treat me to a can of juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:20.96,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,That's more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:24.88,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Since I really didn't do anything so meaningful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:29.64,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Listen. I can grant any wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:32.81,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I have something that allows that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:37.02,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,So don't hesitate and say something you really wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:40.19,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,What is that? Something like a genie's lamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:43.19,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Not a lamp, but that's what I was told.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:43.98,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,By who?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:46.28,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:48.11,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:51.78,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You're a real strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:53.08,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.79,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,And a romantic, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:58.50,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I don't believe in those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.63,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:02.88,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming all the way to say thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:05.21,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,It's great to see that you've recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:06.59,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Bye. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:10.84,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.43,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Misae, who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:14.93,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,He's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:17.06,Default,Girls,0,0,0,,Did you switch from Igarashi-kun to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:17.52,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Do...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:20.90,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Don't wait in front of the school gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.90,0:15:22.61,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,You're... You're hurting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:25.73,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You made Saki and Yuki misunderstand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:27.49,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,What are you going to do if a rumor starts?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:29.24,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Misunderstand what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:32.62,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Look. You're a boy and I'm a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:33.83,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Don't you have any imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:38.46,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Ah, I got it. You like Igarashi-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:41.42,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Aren't you really direct?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:44.00,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,You're really beautiful, so I'm sure it'll work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:46.34,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! Let's ask him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.88,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:49.51,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:54.22,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Why must I ask him out with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:56.85,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Th-That hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:16:00.23,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Hey! You came to grant my wish, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:02.10,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,So why are you getting in my way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:05.86,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Then can the wish be to get married to Igarashi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.07,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:11.36,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:12.78,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:15.37,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You can't manipulate other people's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.12,0:16:20.83,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:24.13,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,You didn't have to do that all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:26.25,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I told you not to wait at the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:29.59,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,You're really being bothered by him, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:31.09,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Shima-kun, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:33.80,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,You see, Misae has someone she likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:36.39,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,If Igarashi-kun sees this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:37.35,Default,Iga,0,0,0,,Did you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:40.93,Default,Iga,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Sagara's boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.64,Default,Iga,0,0,0,,Introduce me, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:45.48,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,N-No! He isn't! He's nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:50.86,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I hope he really got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:56.37,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,It's fine. I'm sure Igarashi-kun will come to like you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.45,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You're really strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:01.46,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:07.13,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You don't get jealous or annoyed even if I like another boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:08.63,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:13.05,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I think I'm just slow at those kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:19.01,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I don't dislike those kinds of things about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:22.85,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,It's nice how pure you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:41.50,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Do you want to catch a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:46.04,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Why don't you at least have an umbrella with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:48.63,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I didn't think it would start raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:53.05,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Why am I taking care of someone like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:53.97,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:58.30,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,If you're going to apologize,\Nthen don't make me take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:01.56,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Here. I borrowed a jersey for you, so change into these.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:02.02,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.35,0:18:05.35,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:09.40,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,If you can grant anything,\Ncouldn't you have stopped the rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:11.07,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:14.90,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I can only grant one wish, and it's for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:19.32,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I don't understand why you're so grateful to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:21.62,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You don't even remember what I said to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:26.33,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,It's probably the more fact that you\Ntalked to me than what you said to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:28.75,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Since you're very optimistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:30.92,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I hear that a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:35.13,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I think I was able to try because I met someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:37.93,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,So it is all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:45.31,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,It's time for class, so I've got to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:47.64,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Sneak out later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:48.27,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:58.86,Default,Iga,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Sagara's boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:01.32,Default,Iga,0,0,0,,Waiting for her again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:04.83,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Um, I'm not Sagara-san's boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:05.87,Default,Iga,0,0,0,,You aren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:09.83,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,No. Apparently she already has someone she likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:15.63,Default,Iga,0,0,0,,Hey, can you do a favor for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:25.39,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You look so gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:28.64,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Did you really catch a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:31.77,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Then what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:32.90,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Is something troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:36.61,Default,Iga,0,0,0,,I know how Sagara feels about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:39.57,Default,Iga,0,0,0,,But as you see, I already have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:42.91,Default,Iga,0,0,0,,So can you drop a hint to her about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:46.16,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,You're too nice to everyone, Igarashi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:48.37,Default,Iga,0,0,0,,What can I do? It's how I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:52.21,Default,Iga,0,0,0,,So please. While hurting her as little as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:55.75,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Hey, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:57.67,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Talk to your big sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:01.30,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Could you possibly be in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:03.76,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:05.35,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.93,0:20:08.06,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I pulled that one out of thin air.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.98,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Then why do you look so depressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:18.61,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,That's because I have sad news for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.99,0:20:20.11,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:23.91,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,She has another boy she likes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:28.37,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,...but that other boy already has a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:31.96,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I was asked by him to pass that on to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:34.54,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Sounds like a drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:37.00,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,But that's a chance for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:45.26,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,{\fs72.9}If you comfort her when she's depressed from the shock of a broken heart, she might come to like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:47.51,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Come on, Shima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:49.85,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Stop being depressed and think positively.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:50.89,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:52.35,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,This is a great chance for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:54.02,Default-alt,Shi,0,0,0,,I can't possibly think like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.11,0:20:59.53,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,If you were in my shoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:02.53,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,...could you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:03.57,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Could you think like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:05.99,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,When you like that person so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:11.45,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,Could you think of it as an opportunity when the person is broken-hearted?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:13.92,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:19.88,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Girls around me all think positively like that, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:41.40,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Shima-kun... What you said just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.95,0:21:44.95,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:47.12,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I'm such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:53.25,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Why are you the one crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:54.75,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I don't know.
