Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.93,0:23:48.94,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,That was the name of the person dearest to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.15,0:24:01.33,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,We spent much time together,\Nand he left me with his last wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.66,0:24:07.25,Default,Shi,0,0,0,,I came to grant that wish.
